00:17:25,230 --> 00:17:25,920
You may leave.

359
00:17:26,450 --> 00:17:26,980
Yes.

360
00:17:29,710 --> 00:17:30,650
Brother Su,

361
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:33,000
