372
00:18:01,430 --> 00:18:02,530
All right.

373
00:18:03,070 --> 00:18:04,750
Brother Su, you come all the way here.

374
00:18:05,030 --> 00:18:06,470
From the manor outside the city,

375
00:18:06,620 --> 00:18:08,280
I bring you

