00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:42,600
The Administrator of Luozhou is a fifth-rank official.

389
00:18:43,780 --> 00:18:44,930
Su Wuming

390
00:18:45,390 --> 00:18:46,420
can make a fortune from now.

