00:25:35,990 --> 00:25:36,490
Come out!

546
00:25:40,460 --> 00:25:41,580
Who are you?

547
00:25:41,870 --> 00:25:43,340
How dare you break into my mansion?

548
00:25:45,390 --> 00:25:46,310
How does this place

