551
00:25:50,340 --> 00:25:50,950
Niu Su.

552
00:25:51,070 --> 00:25:52,210
Who are you?

553
00:25:52,840 --> 00:25:55,720
[Little Beggar, Niu Su]

554
00:25:52,900 --> 00:25:54,100
I heard you say

